Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（学生食堂暑假期间休息）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}由于长期受到恐怖袭击的民众的情绪日益不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}由GGP指挥的反恐特种机动部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}通称"白色Ride队"的投入法在议会上高票通过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}至于其具体投入的时间  目前还正处于讨论阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}既然恐怖分子使用了机动性能优良的Rideback
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}我认为投入警用Ride作为对抗手段可谓是大势所趋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}我们现在必须考虑的是如何防止恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热成这样子  还真亏你能做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得我说过社团活动中止了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以命令我的 只有我所认可的那个男人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}"白色Ride"在装备方面 与其说它是警用车辆 倒不如就说它是种兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}我忧虑的会不会因此 警方而军队化等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}谢谢您的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我骑着也没能作出那样的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那孩子却做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}我没法随心所欲操纵的那玩意儿却让初学者的琳给降伏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是个什么玩意儿 Fuego
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道也没关系 这和你们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会没关系 我们不是Rideback部的伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我有权知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:49.74,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:49.74,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:51.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:51.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上机车 马力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}试着去感受心的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞跃吧！尽你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸腾有如泉涌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:05.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:05.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我们的周遭布满陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用泪水洗去血染的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:12.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:12.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让双眼避开所有的蛊惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:15.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:15.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之风会引领我们向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:36.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:36.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波涛汹涌的世界里找寻指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背骑的身影穿梭其间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们需要的是你们的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去创造属于我们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:58.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
